The '''Death Eye''', also known as the '''PHANTOM''', is an enemy from ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It is a [[fixed encounter]] the party must face before they can access the lower levels of the [[Chaos Shrine (Final Fantasy)|Chaos Shrine]]. It can also appear as a random encounter on the final floor of the Chaos Shrine in version where encounters are enabled on that floor.

