== Battle ==
Due to its low [[HP (stat)|HP]], the Death Eye is typically not a threat. However, it can break resistances via [[Dispel (Final Fantasy)|Dispel]], then follow up with several status and [[instant death]] attacks. Using [[Diaga (Final Fantasy)|Diaga]] or [[Firaga (Final Fantasy)|Firaga]] is recommended to dispose of it quickly.

