==Behind the scenes==
[[File:PHANTOM from FFI Famicom sprite.png|PHANTOM's original Famicom sprite.|thumb]]
Much like the [[Evil Eye (Final Fantasy)|EYE]], in the game's original Japanese release the PHANTOM, then named {{J|デスビホルダー|Desubihorudā|Death Beholder|fmt=j (r)}}, so resembled the Beholders from ''Dungeons & Dragons'' that Nintendo redesigned the shared sprite between the two monsters before bringing the game to the US.
{{clear}}

